{"tid":612940,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卡拉斯高：去中超唔係為錢！","createTime":"2018-04-01T08:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T12:16:01.000Z","uid":4661,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f8e7f0e9f9a9510fa7f32b4abce8c3053a4a81a4","tid":612940,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://e00-marca.uecdn.es/p/110/sp/11000/thumbnail/entry_id/0_2kldhdb7/version/100022/height/407\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fe00-marca.uecdn.es%2Fp%2F110%2Fsp%2F11000%2Fthumbnail%2Fentry_id%2F0_2kldhdb7%2Fversion%2F100022%2Fheight%2F407&h=8a0a2b0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=6N4fQOJwYRzHO2b2gU6NwsVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=ce23382e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】恩歷克卡拉斯高向批評還擊，指轉投中超是為了上陣時間，而不是向錢看。<br />\n<br />\n恩歷克卡拉斯高（Yannick Carrasco）在1月離開了馬德里體育會，加盟中超升班馬大連一方，結果後者在中超開季3連敗，而且1球不入。他24歲就離開歐洲球壇，登陸中超，難免引來貪錢的批評。<br />\n<br />\n這名比利時國腳說：「在足球世界，當你轉會的時候，不論在任何情況，都會有人批評。在人生之中，你經常都要作出艱難的決定，就像我之前一樣。事實是，我沒有足夠的上陣時間，我需要轉會。」<br />\n<br />\n「世界盃決賽周在今個夏天就舉行，我需要多點比賽時間，有穩定的出場機會，以求爭取在國家隊的位置。」恩歷克卡拉斯高在日前的友賽，為比利時正選上陣鬥沙地阿拉伯，結果大勝4:0。"},{"pid":"437183c8fbecb4c5ff08c817d42fcf9bf8200d3b","tid":612940,"uid":5649,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:55:40.000Z","msg":"卡拉斯高細個既夢想就係加盟大連一方"},{"pid":"bdce7c4e7dfad88d4d6a2c189e3f30835539bdfa","tid":612940,"uid":171901,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:57:20.000Z","msg":"卡拉斯高自小就跟隨父親看中超"},{"pid":"1d4774deaf1a37abc5912010a057dca1eb5cd4aa","tid":612940,"uid":65603,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T08:57:29.000Z","msg":"卡拉斯高：愚人節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3776bb03f9902c43c73d772dd2536738776a4584","tid":612940,"uid":22832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:01:52.